order (dashed line)
results for
$\frac{\lambda_R}{2m^2_f}(\langle\Phi^2(\tau)\rangle-
\langle\Phi^2(0)\rangle) = {\cal{D}}(0,\tau)$,
for $\lambda=10^{-12}$, $\frac{T_i}{T_c}=2$.

