$\tau=6$, as function of $x$,
${\cal{D}}^{(HF)}(x,\tau)$ (solid line), and
${\cal{D}}^{(0)}(x,\tau)$ (dashed line).
$\lambda=10^{-12}$, $\frac{T_i}{T_c}=2$.

